{"tid":1726403,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"日本著名漫畫家松本零士疑中風　在意大利送院","createTime":"2019-11-16T06:49:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-19T05:39:36.000Z","uid":20933,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"85624752a87d63d63b2670bcf4f3c00566654d21","tid":1726403,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T06:49:38.000Z","msg":"正在意大利訪問的日本著名漫畫家松本零士，星期五突然身體不適送院，據報是中風，情況嚴重。<br />\n<br />\n現年81歲的松本零土，在都靈出席其作品在意大利播映40周年紀念活動，他星期五抵達預定上映作品《銀河鐵道999》的電影院，但因身體不適，返回酒店休息，據報之後緊急送院。<br />\n<br />\n松本零土1971年開始在雜誌上連載描寫年輕人在東京的貧窮生活的漫畫，嶄露頭角。<br />\n<br />\n他其後多部作品，包括《千年女王》、《宇宙戰艦大和號》和《銀河鐵道999》等大受歡迎，更被改編為動畫電影。"},{"pid":"1178d7cf806f7d67aa6a4b31725d946a803c7278","tid":1726403,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T06:49:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1492599-20191116.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1492599-20191116.htm&d=x8osXdNjm17U7TcHCf5EXoeonPPUtn1HApnj2AcFxYA%3D&h=e7f1784f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1492599-20191116.htm&h=0307d0fa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1492599-20191116.htm</a>"},{"pid":"3e84ec608bc55723b3334dfbd803baba654cf18c","tid":1726403,"uid":96648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T06:53:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12f5d8009121dc89c923637644dbaaa107510bf4","tid":1726403,"uid":49391,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T07:10:12.000Z","msg":"幾鍾意大和號<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/haUzqxN.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhaUzqxN.gif&h=863fdf8b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3hS5xcW.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3hS5xcW.